    &lt;li&gt;EncontraoTropical&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/MutGamb-revista-de-cultura-digital-brasileira&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Revista MutGamb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://rede.metareciclagem.org/blog/17-12-09/MutGamb-no-Knight-News-Challenge&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Mutgamb no Knight News Challenge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
